Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.50,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,First time ever on Gaki no Tsukai ya Arahende!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:07.44,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Appreciation meeting for "The Bus Hijacker Returns" starring Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.64,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't it... a bit cold here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought the coldness was from the AC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But it's coming from the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:18.51,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's the AC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.21,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The AC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.63,Endo,,0,0,0,,No way it's from the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(519.75,48)}note: from left to right, up to down: Matsumoto Hitoshi, Hamada Masatoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(519.75,87)}Fujiwara Kazuhiro, Imoto Takafumi, Endo Shozo, Tsukitei Hosei, Tanaka Naoki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Should come from here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.53,Endo,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:22.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The movie is not on yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.67,Endo,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,After all it's not a lame movie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(548.438,43.5)\4c&H030304&\4a&HFF&\b1} {\fs37.5}note: "cold" and "lame" are both "samui" in japanese{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not lame at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie "The Bus Hijacker Returns" starring Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Has been released this year (2017) in July!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a certain reason for why this movie was made...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:42.07,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I actually felt like taking part on it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:44.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,For real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:45.27,Endo,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.71,Endo,,0,0,0,,Before this movie I worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,A previous project (Busjack)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:48.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:51.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,But it didn't really sell good at all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,But we got to joke about it on No-Laughing Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:53.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\fad(200,0)\pos(519.75,79.5)\4c&H030304&\4a&HFF&}lower screen: {\c&H0088FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}The first solo-movie Endo starred in, "Busjack" {\c&H0019FF&\3c&H000000&}was revealed {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HFF7C2B&}to be the 40805th movie on Amazon DVD popularity ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,And its popularity suddenly rose up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was funny so it got popular, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.25,Endo,,0,0,0,,And then the two of you told me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.59,Endo,,0,0,0,,That it would be nice to have a sequel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:03.59,Endo,,0,0,0,,So it felt like I had to make a "return"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We talked about this on a costume talk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\fad(200,200)\pos(519.75,79.5)\4c&H030304&\4a&HFF&}lower screen: {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HFF7C2B&}The day after Downtown {\c&H0019FF&}stated they would take part on a possible sequel, {\3c&H000000&\c&H61F5F7&}"The Bus Hijacker Return" {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HFF7C2B&}'s production was decided
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:05.03,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.03,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Yeah, on September, last year
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:09.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I really thought about taking part in it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,On the other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san was more like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:14.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"Enough of that crap"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:15.54,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,He's so rude
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.27,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I haven't said such things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.57,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He said something about it being pointless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:22.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,After all if we are together we're Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:26.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even if we're attending a funeral, we want to act as Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.88,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it became a big topic on the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.78,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Just look at this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.59,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,This is an article from Yahoo news
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:35.46,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,"Even though it's Endo's movie premiere, the theater seats are empty"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.99,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,"A resentful complaint from Downtown"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.99,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.70,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen this article, take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:45.67,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,At what Matsumoto recently tweeted
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:47.67,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry Endo, my stomach hurts"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.44,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,What do you mean with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all I'm feeling sorry for it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The fact is... it was too funny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought "why is it funny?" and felt sorry for him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:58.81,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There was also... that guy, Onigiri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That huge Yoshimoto comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:06.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He actually paid to go see your movie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:09.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And he was like "man, that was really hilarious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:09.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah he said it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:14.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And he was like "Matsumoto-san please go see it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In the end I didn't go, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:17.37,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,He invited you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Lots of people liked it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.37,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.47,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.07,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,By the way, here's the cast chart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.07,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,It's just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.28,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Endo-san plays Noboru Komiya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.28,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,That's the main role
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.71,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,His colleague is Kurosawa from Morisanchu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:31.71,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.71,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,And his younger colleague is Iwao-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.71,Endo,,0,0,0,,There's also Honkon-san playing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,A Yakuza boss
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.59,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Actually the role
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.59,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Ozawa-san is playing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.96,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Was planned for Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:43.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh? Was it not Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.89,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,No, it was you Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.75,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,The mysterious man is played by Jimmy-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.75,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,And this role was supposed to be Hamada's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You are similar comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.14,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I just agreed to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They are similar, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:02.01,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you look it up on the GPS their field of activity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.41,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is pretty much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.35,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.45,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,By the way, we also have the producer Ohta-san, today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.75,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(531.563,45)\4c&H030304&\4a&HFF&}text: "The Bus Hijacker Returns" 's director: Ohta Masayuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.09,other,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.32,other,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,How dare you came here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.32,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Please don't mind him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.53,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,It looks like the reviews aren't really praising it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.17,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.25,other,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a flop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.54,Endo,,0,0,0,,Even after all that motion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.24,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,What could the reason be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:33.63,other,,0,0,0,,I had this conversation with members of the staff too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.83,other,,0,0,0,,And they agreed that Endo's acting is kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.62,Endo,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.21,other,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Was it my acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You should have know that from the first movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So for example what is it? The acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.70,other,,0,0,0,,Yes they said it was kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.66,other,,0,0,0,,Unskilled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\fad(0,200)\4c&H030304&\4a&HFF&\pos(548.438,40.5)}note: "kusai" means "smelly", but it also means "unskilled", "poor" figuratively
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Unskilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Smelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His acting smelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.85,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,I've talked about this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.30,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,To Ohta-san too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:56.63,Tanaka/girl,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:00.73,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,As you watch the movie and you think Endo's acting is unskilled
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.87,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,You can press the "that smells!" button under your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.87,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,You can press it every time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.48,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,You think his acting is poor
