Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H61F5F7&\4c&H030304&\4a&HF4&\pos(178.875,784.5)}Screening Rules
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(545.063,874.5)}If they feel like Endo's performance is {\c&H0014DD&\3c&HFFFFFF&}"smelly"{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}, they'll push the button
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.18,Endo,,0,0,0,,We're going to watch it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.41,Endo,,0,0,0,,I mean, the whole "it smells" thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's what the producer said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,You sure it's okay? It's not a good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.80,other,,0,0,0,,Nah it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is it ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.82,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's ok...?
