Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.78,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Because I respect them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Is he judging them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}I have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,No no, listen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,We're almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:39.13,other2,,0,0,0,,Sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,Drive us back from where we set off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.85,other,,0,0,0,,Ok, count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.15,Jimmy/Iwao,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.03,actress,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.57,Jimmy/Iwao,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's here, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:02.94,other,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}What is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.34,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Get away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Kashira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.81,other,,0,0,0,,I got your call
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}What a great surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}...Or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Joichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}This man is not Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:27.53,other,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}I made a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}The current Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Got a plastic surgery and changed his face
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.91,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Here's a picture of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm astonished
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:47.05,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}I am... Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.49,Endo,,0,0,0,,I am Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.33,Endo,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha tryna say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are ya trying to act like one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.80,actress,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.80,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.15,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:08.14,other,,0,0,0,,You-- are you trying to boss me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a public safety employee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.08,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,As long as there's a criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.08,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,I can't just let it go by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.75,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,That's just it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Shige...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}#@&£%!=§
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.69,Endo,,0,0,0,,I can't hear a single line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming after, it's finally time for the climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Man, that was my last chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}And I've failed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,We're almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.28,actress,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.28,actress,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.39,actress,,0,0,0,,It was the best thrilling tour
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.02,actress,,0,0,0,,We've ever experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.32,actress,,0,0,0,,Well, I had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.56,Tanaka/girl,,0,0,0,,We could experience something unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.40,actress,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}And that's all thanks to Komiya-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.71,Endo,,0,0,0,,All of you... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no need to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.05,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Listen to me: I am Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.19,other,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.19,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}I'm about to change my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Which is now to release
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}All of my hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}You're free, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They're pressing it accordingly to the clapping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.68,other,,0,0,0,,Your friends are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.25,actress,,0,0,0,,Please go, Komiya-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.63,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Man, this is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So in the end Kurosawa..?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.30,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he can reach her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.45,actress,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.45,Endo,,0,0,0,,I did the bus hijacking tour
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.49,actress,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.49,Endo,,0,0,0,,And I was able to save everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.72,actress,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}You did it with your own strength
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}That's because you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.45,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}Until the very end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.17,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}@#%&)(\-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.99,Endo,,0,0,0,,I can't hear a goddamn line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.53,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's way too noisy in here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is the last part, I promise, it's almost over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.20,Jimmy/Iwao,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.60,actress,,0,0,0,,What's wrong Yanagita-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.35,Jimmy/Iwao,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.35,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550.125,661.5)}...What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.06,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's over now, we're done
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,As long as you're on screen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,You press it even if only my name is showing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.47,Endo,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: total of pressed buttons & a word from Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.47,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think that everyone around him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Seem to have given their best at it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Doesn't really apply to Endo or Honkon-san, though
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:39.05,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,To be honest I couldn't hear a single line from Honkon-san
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:41.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He was on screen too much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:41.99,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,He sucked pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.09,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Now it's finally time to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.23,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,How many times you've pressed the "it sucks" button
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:49.53,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Let's show the results
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.26,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.43,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Your summed up total counts 2278 times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:55.17,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,Housei-san pressed it the most
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.97,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I really enjoyed this, to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.77,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I'd love to have an "it sucks" button like that in theaters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It would be something new, I think so too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I agree, it's great
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:05.88,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,Have this, Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:08.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,Sorry, and thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:08.32,Tanaka/girl,,0,0,0,,Is that..?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:10.32,Inomoto/other,,0,0,0,,A promotion from our protagonist Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:12.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It will be nice if you promote it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like, talking about why it's worth watching
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:13.99,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:18.79,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really... everybody, we gave our best to film this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.79,Endo,,0,0,0,,And worked for three days straight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.53,Endo,,0,0,0,,And we got it screened on theaters too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:29.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,So if you wish to see more in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:32.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,Please, consider buying this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.31,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's out on September the 1st! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:46.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Which was this movie's signature phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:48.75,Endo,,0,0,0,,When I recognize my role as Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm Komiya and I've been mistaken
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:54.19,Endo,,0,0,0,,After everyone realizes that, I say "I'll lead this bus"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:55.63,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Was that part there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:56.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Of course it was
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:59.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,You were just pressing too much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.30,Fujiwara,,0,0,0,,You didn't even notice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:03.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,There was, I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:03.20,Tanaka/girl,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We were too shocked
